{"tid":1948841,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★太古城三房戶1490萬沽　原業主持貨15年賺千萬","createTime":"2020-03-29T09:12:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T13:46:05.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a94023b1d8d5c0add5698400a33ebc4b46e55b1a","tid":1948841,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T09:12:24.000Z","msg":"中原趙鴻運表示，鰂魚涌太古城東山閣極高層A室，實用面積760方呎，三房連套房間隔，坐向東北望海景，早前以1,700萬港元叫價放盤，其後下調至1,500多萬元，最後以1,490萬元連租售出，呎價19,605元。<br />\n<br />\n原業主於2005年3月以488萬元買入單位，一直作收租用途，現沽貨帳面獲利1,002萬元，單位升值超過2倍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200329/bkn-20200329160905126-0329_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200329%2Fbkn-20200329160905126-0329_00842_001.html&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJe1Ln0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=909561ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200329/bkn-20200329160905126-0329_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"85ef890a19e0bc1a6a451fae7e970432df115480","tid":1948841,"uid":213877,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T09:14:03.000Z","msg":"住到舊先賣，一樣有人接手"},{"pid":"6f10030ed37e10b0e7552c52a4aae7c4bb68d91e","tid":1948841,"uid":237562,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T09:14:06.000Z","msg":"咁就執過千"},{"pid":"380c2eba6da491103b2727754d8e2e09b63b84c7","tid":1948841,"uid":15084,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85ef890a19e0bc1a6a451fae7e970432df115480","tid":1948841,"uid":213877,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T09:14:03.000Z","msg":"住到舊先賣，一樣有人接手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T09:15:56.000Z","msg":"收租比人住到舊<br />\n轉手都可能係同一租客"},{"pid":"885e76ce3145de20fd39fb982380a178cfe85b94","tid":1948841,"uid":170335,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T09:18:32.000Z","msg":"一千萬等於月入二萬做四十年"},{"pid":"51d1140c41d4a21596b62f09a9c628055036aec5","tid":1948841,"uid":6352,